Alterations in heart rate variability are associated with abnormal
myocardial perfusion
Anish S. Shah a, Rachel Lampert b, Jack Goldberg c,d, J. Douglas Bremner e,f,g, Lian Li h, Marc D. Thames i,
Viola Vaccarino h,i, Amit J. Shah ⁎ g,h,i,
